{"tid":858343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【施政報告】人工島被指「官話OK就OK」 林鄭：唔好用馬主席口吻同我講","createTime":"2018-10-11T17:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T00:37:38.000Z","uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb567f13193a62ff78e7af77cf42f5b02320593b","tid":858343,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"新一份《施政報告》提出在東大嶼山海域填海1700公頃造地的「明日大嶼」計劃，掀起爭議。特首林鄭月娥出席電台聯播節目時，被主持問到市民會覺得「官員話OK就OK」，林鄭隨即笑言：「唔好用馬主席（港鐵主席馬時亨）嘅口吻同我講。」她指，研究認為可提供多公頃建屋，呼籲外界不要用陰謀論看待事件，免得「令到官員唔敢做事」。<br />\n　「明日大嶼」計劃涉及填海面積達1700公頃，遠超上屆政府提出的1000公頃，但與團結香港基金近日提出的2200公頃接近。林鄭月娥被問到有否參考團結香港基金結果，她強調：「無同團結香港基金對數」，並指雙方均以科學性作工程研究，包括航道、水流等，故此得出相近數字不難理解。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wQMWum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wQMWum.jpg&h=29ff66fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52f666d5c99e5feb960c4b0759706c6340741d46","tid":858343,"uid":8187,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T18:25:49.000Z","msg":"成份施政報告都係陰謀<br />\n又唔比人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710dc000e872cdfeb12c4b0051f8bab8e58fb8a0","tid":858343,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dddcbd261ec81d4c5199449045bdc32c165204","tid":858343,"uid":26329,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:04:31.000Z","msg":"馬屎坑既口吻你唔鍾意聽 難道香港市民鍾意聽?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8ac834f4257e010d4f4ecfc4a907b8c2c55177","tid":858343,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:22:37.000Z","msg":"陽謀了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756604bdad857365874d5340076064162b0ee64f","tid":858343,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,